Description: iTunes remote control applet for Ubuntu
 An remote control for iTunes, integrated with the indicator-applet in Ubuntu.
 .
 Allows basic remote control of an iTunes instance. Supports play, pause, 
 next/previous tracks and display currently playing track info. Can be controlled 
 from the indicator-applet menu or directly from the keyboard.
 .
 Uses the daap & dacp protocols, and does not require any additional software 
 to be installed on the remote host.
